Sentence: Visible single-photon detection has been demonstrated in MgB nanowires with a T c as high as 31 K (compared to 39 K in the bulk material) and an operating temperature as high as 11 K [9, 10].

Name: YBCO
Sentence: The YBCO device consists of a 10 nm thick, 65 nm wide, and nm long nanowire patterned via argon ion milling through a hard carbon mask.
